"{\"uid\": \"canberratimes.com.au-story-8719920-noemie-fox-is-an-olympic-champion-like-her-sister\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Your digital subscription includes access to content from all our websites in your region.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 90, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Access unlimited news content and The Canberra Times app.\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Canberra Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Premium subscribers also enjoy interactive puzzles and access to the digital version of our print edition - Today's Paper.\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Noemie Fox has stepped out of the shadow of her triple Olympic champion sister Jessica to win a gold medal of her own in the kayak cross to complete a clean sweep of women's canoe events for their family.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 274, \"end\": 284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noemie Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\"}, {\"begin\": 353, \"end\": 360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9999768058498885, \"rank\": 2.2414171052529643e-05, \"text\": \"Jessica\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loginor signup to continue reading  The 27-year-old has collected Australia's 13th gold medal of the Paris Games with an unstoppable display in the new Olympic whitewater event.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 546, \"end\": 555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9986238199431716, \"rank\": 0.001138119038532333, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fox won every round before taking out the four-paddler final on Monday at the Vaires-sur-Marne Nautical Stadium.\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 659, \"end\": 662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9919130749333717, \"rank\": 0.007047980453068543, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 737, \"end\": 753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaires-sur-Marne\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.198375117344811e-17, \"text\": \"Vaires-sur-Marne\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaires-sur-Marne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaires-sur-Marne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fox crossed the line ahead of France's Angele Hug with Great Britain's \\u00a0reigning world champion Kimberley Woods winning bronze.\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 773, \"end\": 776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9919130749333717, \"rank\": 0.007047980453068543, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 803, \"end\": 809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9816519351103982, \"rank\": 0.011158882103506833, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 828, \"end\": 841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.8387227262149672, \"rank\": 0.11361133797725083, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 869, \"end\": 884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberley_Woods\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kimberley Woods\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberley_Woods\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberley_Woods\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Woods held the lead but struggled to get around an upstream gate late in the course, allowing Fox to power to victory.\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9919130749333717, \"rank\": 0.007047980453068543, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jessica won the C1 and K1 Olympics titles - to bring her medal tally to six from four Games - before being eliminated early in the kayak cross.\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1022, \"end\": 1029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9999768058498885, \"rank\": 2.2414171052529643e-05, \"text\": \"Jessica\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\"}, {\"begin\": 1038, \"end\": 1040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_Canoe_Slalom_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.9976541155657427, \"rank\": 0.002230048408997736, \"text\": \"C1\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_Canoe_Slalom_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_Canoe_Slalom_World_Cup\"}, {\"begin\": 1045, \"end\": 1047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K-1\", \"score\": 0.9999999993583515, \"rank\": 5.449553075655861e-10, \"text\": \"K1\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K-1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K-1\"}, {\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wrestling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympics titles\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wrestling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wrestling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their mother Myriam Fox-Jerusalmi is also an Olympic medallist, winning a K1 bronze for France at the 1996 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1180, \"end\": 1186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myriam_Montemayor_Cruz\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 1.0358553042873838e-12, \"text\": \"Myriam\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myriam_Montemayor_Cruz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myriam_Montemayor_Cruz\"}, {\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9816519351103982, \"rank\": 0.011158882103506833, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's crazy that it's mine,\\\" Noemie said of the gold medal.\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You do not really dare to dream this big, but I really did this time and I dared to dream to get to the Olympics and then to get to that final.\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I saw in the last up (gate) that I was first, it was pure joy - there is no words to describe that feeling.\\\"\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fox was joined in the water by 30-year-old Jessica, who jumped in to celebrate after cheering her sibling all the way down the course.\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1608, \"end\": 1611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9919130749333717, \"rank\": 0.007047980453068543, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Noemie has long been a world-class paddler, she's never been able to compete in an Olympics before with her superstar sister taking the only Australian selection spot available.\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1927, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1891, \"end\": 1901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.990133254557423, \"rank\": 0.009624718505324871, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The younger sibling said there were many times she considered giving the sport away, such was her sister's dominance.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 2046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the addition of the splash and dash event in Paris opened up another spot for Noemie to qualify alongside Jessica, who helped her prepare for the selection regatta.\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2097, \"end\": 2102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999158717, \"rank\": 8.407682631326137e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2158, \"end\": 2165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9999768058498885, \"rank\": 2.2414171052529643e-05, \"text\": \"Jessica\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am her biggest cheerleader, just like she's mine,\\\" Noemie said.\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2284, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To watch her win two golds and then to have her as my biggest cheerleader, it's a fairytale ending.\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2386, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's the greatest of all time in our sport ... watching her win, it's just such a privilege and inspiration and it really fuelled me.\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When someone like that really believes in you and tells you 'you have got it', you have got to go and get it.\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I got my moment and it's my medal and we are walking away with three gold medals in our family, which is insane.\\\"\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2751, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jessica said she was proud to see her sister achieve her dream.\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2753, \"end\": 2760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9999768058498885, \"rank\": 2.2414171052529643e-05, \"text\": \"Jessica\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was so nervous, I just wanted her to do a good race \\u2026 she nailed it,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2900, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just in awe of her \\u2026 she's an Olympic champion and she has worked so hard for that, I am so happy for her.\\\"\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 3015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If the Fox family were a nation, they would sit in 16th spot on the overall medal table at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3024, \"end\": 3027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9919130749333717, \"rank\": 0.007047980453068543, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian Associated Press  Daily  Today's top stories curated by our news team.\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Also includes evening update.\", \"from\": 3208, \"to\": 3237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As it happens  Do not miss updates on news about the Public Service.\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3307, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekdays  Grab a quick bite of today's latest news from around the region and the nation.\", \"from\": 3309, \"to\": 3398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekdays  Catch up on the news of the day and unwind with great reading for your evening.\", \"from\": 3400, \"to\": 3489, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekly  Get the editor's insights: what's happening & why it matters.\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Twice weekly  Stay in the know on news that matters to you with twice weekly newsletters from The Senior.\", \"from\": 3562, \"to\": 3667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekly  Going out or staying in?\",